column5: Several times this morning I've lost posts because I keep gettin' either 'PAGE NOT AVAILABLE,' or "PAGE EXPIRED?' I'm not doing ANYTHING DIFFERENT . . . .     wazzup ?
Clear your OFC cookies, Steve and try again. No issues here that I can see. We went to a new server the other day, so your cookies or DNS cache may be buggered.
It's not just you Steve...I was posting and got a "Cannot find server" for about 5 minutes, then the site came back up.
I had the same thing late last night but it seems fine this morning.  Just slow changing pages.
ya ive been getting the cannot find server. i would try agian a few seconds later and it would load up, it was very slow mind you. now it seems to be working fine.
